### 🔑 快速审批操作

#### 方式一：Dashboard图形界面
1. 打开 Dashboard → Content Drafts
2. 筛选 `status = draft` + `batch = v2`
3. 勾选要审批的内容 → 点击"批准发布"
4. 系统自动复制到 `~/.aida/mock-publish/`

#### 方式二：命令行（如果你更喜欢）
```bash
# 审批单个门店v2版本
openclaw bps-update entityType=content-draft entityId=content-cs-ktv-20260310-v2 publishReady=true

# 审批全部v2版本（5个门店）
openclaw bps-update entityType=content-draft entityId=content-wh-tea-20260310-v2 publishReady=true
openclaw bps-update entityType=content-draft entityId=content-wh-ktv-20260310-v2 publishReady=true
openclaw bps-update entityType=content-draft entityId=content-cs-mj-20260310-v2 publishReady=true
openclaw bps-update entityType=content-draft entityId=content-cs-tea-20260310-v2 publishReady=true
openclaw bps-update entityType=content-draft entityId=content-cs-ktv-20260310-v2 publishReady=true
```

